 (composer)|Stuart MacRae]] and Louise Welsh \u2013 ''Anthropocene''<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/jan/25/anthropocene-review-stuart-macrae-scottish-opera | title=Anthropocene review \u2013 MacRae's arctic adventure delivers operatic thrills | work=The Guardian | author=Rowena Smith | date=25 January 2019 | accessdate=27 January 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Gabriel Prokofiev]] and [[David Pountney]] \u2013 ''Elizabetta''<ref>[https://www.theater-regensburg.de/spielplan/details/elizabetta/ Theater Regensburg page on ''Elizabetta'']</ref>\n* [[Philip Venables]] and Ted Huffman \u2013 ''Denis & Katya''<ref>[https://www.operaphila.org/whats-on/on-stage-2019-2020/denis-katya/ Opera Philadelphia page on ''Denis & Katya'']</ref>\n\n==Musical theatre==\n*''[[Only Fools and Horses The Musical]]'', by [[Paul Whitehouse]] and [[Jim Sullivan (writer)|Jim Sullivan]], with additional music by [[Chas Hodges]] and [[John Sullivan (writer)|John Sullivan]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-45783432|title=Only Fools and Horses musical heads for West End|date=8 October 2018|website=BBC News|access-date=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Musical films==\n*''Blinded by the Light'', starring [[Hayley Atwell]] and [[Kulvinder Ghir]], with music by [[Bruce Springsteen]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/04/blinded-by-the-light-gurinder-chadha-bruce-springsteen-blessings-hayley-atwell-cast-first-look-photo-1202362218/|title=Gurinder Chadha\u2019s \u2018Blinded By The Light\u2019 Blessed By Bruce Springsteen; Cast Set|date=April 11, 2018|author=Nancy Tartaglione|website=Deadline|access-date=26 January 2019}}</ref>\n*''[[Cats (2019 film)|Cats]]'', starring [[James Corden]], [[Idris Elba]], [[Ian McKellen]] and [[Judi Dench]], with music by [[Andrew Lloyd Webber]], due for release on 20 December.<ref>[https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cats-movie-gets-december-2019-release-date-1138971 'Cats' Movie Adaptation Sets December 2019 Releas